Build instructions:
  unpack msmtp-1.4.30-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
    unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  ./msmtp*.sh all

This will create:
  msmtp-1.4.30-1.tar.bz2
  msmtp-1.4.30-1-src.tar.bz2

